Package com.risk.orders

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Order
    The interface Order.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Advance
    The type advance
    AdvanceTest
    To Test the Advance card functionality in the game i.e move some armies from one of the current player’s territories (source) to an adjacent territory (target).
    Airlift
    The type Airlift.
    AirliftTest
    To Test the Airlift card functionality in the game i.e advance some armies from one of the current player’s territories to any another territory that is owned by the player.
    Blockade
    The type Blockade
    BlockadeTest
    To Test the blockade card functionality in the game i.e on using blockade card the target territory's army units are tripled and it is made neutral.
    Bomb
    The type Bomb
    BombTest
    To Test the Bomb functionality in the game i.e on using the bomb card, the target country loses half of their army units.
    Deploy
    The Command Pattern Class for Deploy Order
    Diplomacy
    Type Diplomacy
    DiplomacyTest
    To Test the Diplomacy functionality in the game i.e on using the diplomacy card, the target player and current player can not attack on each other.
    OrdersTestSuits
    Test suite for Orders tests.
